text: Glad it was helpful! Yeah sounds good, let me know if you want me to take a look. When it's ready, if you like I can ask someone in our tracking/matchmove department to give their thoughts?

That’d be great, thanks! 
I mentioned you when I was talking to my matchmoving teacher, and apparently he used to work at Milk a few years ago, but I think it might’ve been before you started. 

I think some of the footage he gave me to practice tracking was actually from when he worked at Milk too, so they might even recognise the tracked scenes!
